data.description: Located near the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, and all on ONE level, this fabulous Sturbridge home features 4 bedrooms and 3 baths!  Newly painted interior and exterior, new carpet installed in front bedrooms and all new windows in front of home in 2021. Beautiful living spaces include an entry foyer, a dining room and a spacious great room with built-ins, recessed lighting and gas fireplace. Other rooms include a large breakfast room and a chef's dream of a kitchen offering granite countertops, a granite work island, numerous cabinets and stainless/black appliances. The master suite is spacious and has double closets, double vanities, a garden tub and separate shower.  A beautifully updated bath serves 2 of the guest bedrooms with an ensuite bath adjoining the 3rd guest bedroom. Exterior features include nice shade trees with a private backyard which is fully fenced, a large patio, 2 car carport with attached storage and the list goes on! Make your appointment today to see this immaculate home!
